{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.19"},"kind":"article","seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.18","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17.1","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.16","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.15","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.14","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.13","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.12","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.11","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.10","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.9","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.8","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.7","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.6","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.5","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.4"],"generated":true}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"There are no steps needed to migrate to 1.19 of the Composable Architecture, but there are a number"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of changes and improvements that have been made to the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Store"},{"type":"text","text":" that one should be aware of."}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Store-internals-rewrite","text":"Store internals rewrite","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The store’s internals have been rewritten to improved performance and to pave the way for future"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"features. While this should not be a breaking change, with any rewrite it is important to thoroughly"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"test your application after upgrading."}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"StateObject-compatibility","text":"StateObject compatibility","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"SwiftUI’s ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@State"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@StateObject"},{"text":" allow a view to own a value or object over time, ensuring that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"when a parent view is recomputed, the view-local state isn’t recreated from scratch.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"One important difference between ","type":"text"},{"code":"@State","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"@StateObject","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is that ","type":"text"},{"code":"@State","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"’s initializer is","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"eager, while ","type":"text"},{"code":"@StateObject","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"‘s is lazy. Because of this, if you initialize a root ","type":"text"},{"code":"Store","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to be held","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in ","type":"text"},{"code":"@State","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", stores will be initialized (and immediately discarded) whenever the parent view’s body","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is computed.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To avoid the creation of these stores, one can now assign the store to a ","type":"text"},{"code":"@StateObject","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", instead:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["struct FeatureView: View {","  @StateObject var store: StoreOf<Feature>","","  init() {","    _store = StateObject(","      \/\/ This expression is only evaluated the first time the parent view is computed.","      wrappedValue: Store(initialState: Feature.State()) {","        Feature()","      }","    )","  }","","  var body: some View { \/* ... *\/ }","}"]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The store’s ","type":"text"},{"code":"ObservableObject","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" conformance does not have any impact on the actual","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"observability of the store. You should continue to rely on the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/ObservableState()","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" macro for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"observation.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"aside","name":"Important","style":"important"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/composablearchitecture\/migratingto1.19"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"title":"Migrating to 1.19","role":"article","modules":[{"name":"ComposableArchitecture"}],"roleHeading":"Article"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Store internals have been rewritten for performance and future features, and are now compatible with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"SwiftUI’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@StateObject"},{"type":"text","text":" property wrapper."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigrationGuides"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":